{"tid":1812508,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警甴一棍打落一個十幾歲既年輕人到","createTime":"2020-01-05T14:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T15:57:27.000Z","uid":175623,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16f733a7ad504f5423e1d81ebbc7be5f70a4d46a","tid":1812508,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"黑警甴一棍打落一個十幾歲既年輕人到個陣 有冇諗過佢都係香港人？ 有冇諗過要積德行善？<br />\n<br />\n所以所有黑警父母腦癌中風 活到過百歲仲未死 黑警自己及其家屬全身潰爛 四肢殘障 愛滋 各不同癌生齊 然後活到90幾歲仲未死<br />\n<br />\n記住人地問你職業個陣大大聲講話自己做香港警察啊 或我有家屬做香港警察啊 否則：你只係連職業都唔敢同人地講既可憐蟲渣垃圾！憑乜撚嘢笑人住公屋？食生命麵包？<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個再講有白警 一律視之為鬼！<br />\n<br />\nbtw 有冇得再差d?"},{"pid":"5243bf4d05f7982ed86f2a9761078ed6e1b1fea7","tid":1812508,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"以上內容參考啤梨哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6873b9c9de16e334d32a2261eaad71a8880b6503","tid":1812508,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"啤梨晚報逢星期一至五 六點至八點 同你分識時事 窮追猛打"},{"pid":"15fda99dc743388572556fb7d6db5e2bbaf657ad","tid":1812508,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"幫推!<br />\n<br />\n依家要多啲文宣呀! 有新玩法 仲有教學同示範tim!<br />\n<br />\n[行動]文宣都十八區開花 A4 label周圍貼 (更新:大量現成圖 即print 即貼!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810856</a>"},{"pid":"26d5353dd937741af43646f54224d426b16191f0","tid":1812508,"uid":258578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e1d52b535a3e55b118b63fe24785ecc364199f2","tid":1812508,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26d5353dd937741af43646f54224d426b16191f0","tid":1812508,"uid":258578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:14:43.000Z"